{
  "description": "A close-up, dynamic image captures the swirling, curling form of a wave just as it's breaking. The water is translucent, showcasing a beautiful blend of blues and whites, with hints of turquoise where the light penetrates. The wave's crest is forming a hollow shape, creating a tube-like structure with air pockets visible within. Sunlight glints off the surface, creating shimmering highlights and accentuating the movement and texture of the water. The base of the wave is darker and more opaque, suggesting depth and power. The composition is dramatic and emphasizes the raw energy of the ocean.",
